rows.label: bf09320100_0010
rows.name: You're the one who hasn't changed.

rows.label: bf09320100_0020
rows.name:
That's exactly why you get in the way
of those who wish to change!

rows.label: bf09320100_0030
rows.name: And why should I have to change?

rows.label: bf09320100_0040
rows.name: If I change, I lose everything.

rows.label: bf09320100_0060
rows.name: Who in their right mind would accept such a fate?!

rows.label: bf09320100_0080
rows.name:
You're weak, old man.
The weakest of us all...
